3. Verify method invocation
Verify that a method invocation produces the expected result.
We create a component with a counter attribute and a method that increments that counter.
We verify that the method invocation increments the counter as expected. 
Note that you cannot directly invoke methods in the component’s controller or helper. 
You can only invoke methods that are exposed as part of the component’s public API with an definition.

